attributes.description:
Visualizations related to the many-shards-snapshots challenge of the elastic/logs track.

Intended to track performance while taking a high amount of snapshot on a cluster that contains a high number of indices/shards.
attributes.title: nightly-elastic-logs/many-shards-snapshots
